  <name>System Companion</name>
  <summary>System health and maintenance dashboard</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      System Companion is a fast, optimized, and beautiful system health & maintenance dashboard for Ubuntu Linux. 
      Built with GTK4 and libadwaita, it provides real-time system monitoring, predictive maintenance alerts, 
      intelligent cleanup recommendations, and performance optimization.
    </p>
    <p>Key features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Real-time CPU, memory, and disk usage monitoring</li>
      <li>Network performance metrics and bandwidth analysis</li>
      <li>System health assessment and service monitoring</li>
      <li>Performance benchmarking and optimization</li>
      <li>Security monitoring and vulnerability scanning</li>
      <li>Automated maintenance and cleanup tools</li>
      <li>Modern GTK4/libadwaita user interface</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
